{
  "_comment": "臨床維度定義（TCGA）。每個 cohort 一份，未來 OSCC 套同格式即可（相同維度沿用、不同維度各自定義、TCGA 沒有的如 ENE 在 OSCC 版加上去）。type=binary 是天然兩組；type=ordinal 是有序多級，使用者可把每個級別指派到 baseline/advanced/ignore。advancedSide 標哪一側帶星號。field 指這個維度需要 clinical 的哪個欄位（該欄不存在或全空 -> 此維度在該範圍不可用，介面自動灰掉）。",
  "dimensions": [
    {
      "id": "sex",
      "name": "Sex",
      "type": "binary",
      "field": "gender",
      "baseline": {
        "label": "Male",
        "values": [
          "MALE",
          "Male",
          "male"
        ]
      },
      "advanced": {
        "label": "Female",
        "values": [
          "FEMALE",
          "Female",
          "female"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "age",
      "name": "Age",
      "type": "binary",
      "field": "age",
      "numericSplit": {
        "cutoff": 60,
        "baselineLabel": "<60",
        "advancedLabel": ">=60"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "alcohol",
      "name": "Alcohol",
      "type": "binary",
      "field": "alcohol_history_documented",
      "baseline": {
        "label": "Alcohol-",
        "values": [
          "NO",
          "No",
          "no"
        ]
      },
      "advanced": {
        "label": "Alcohol+",
        "values": [
          "YES",
          "Yes",
          "yes"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
